Pendulum Effect
 You cannot Pendulum Summon monsters, except "Ritual Beast" or "Sephira" monsters. This effect cannot be negated.

 Monster Effect
 When this card is Normal or Pendulum Summoned: You can target 1 "Ritual Beast" or "Sephira" monster in your Graveyard, except "Sephiram Pilica, the Bold Ritual Beast Tamer"; Special Summon it, but destroy it during the End Phase. You can only Special Summon 1 "Sephiram Pilica, the Bold Ritual Beast Tamer" per turn.
